    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This code sample demonstrates <strong>valerie</strong> being used to validate a form for
gathering someone&rsquo;s favourite foods.</p>

<p>It demonstrates:</p>

<ul>
<li>how the <code>noneOf</code> and <code>not</code> rules can be used</li>
<li>how rules can be chained together</li>
<li>the <code>disabledWhenNotValid</code> binding</li>
</ul>


<!-- more -->


<p>This sample can be seen running
<a href="http://jsfiddle.net/gh/gist/knockout/2.2.1/6203d05150de9baf7015/" title="Favourite Foods Form">here</a> â‡—.</p>

<h2>HTML</h2>

<p><div><script src='https://gist.github.com/6203d05150de9baf7015.js?file=fiddle.html'></script>
<noscript><pre><code>&lt;div id=&quot;sample&quot; class=&quot;form-horizontal&quot;&gt;
     &lt;h2&gt;Favourite Foods&lt;/h2&gt;

    &lt;p&gt;No one likes &lt;strong&gt;brussel sprouts&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;ul data-bind=&quot;foreach: favourites&quot;&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;
            &lt;button data-bind=&quot;click: $root.remove.bind($data, $index)&quot;&gt;-&lt;/button&gt;
            &lt;span data-bind=&quot;text: $data&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;fieldset&gt;
        &lt;button data-bind=&quot;click: add, disabledWhenNotValid: newFavourite&quot;&gt;+&lt;/button&gt;
        &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; data-bind=&quot;value: newFavourite, validationCss: true&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/fieldset&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre></noscript></div>
</p>

<h2>Javascript</h2>

<p><div><script src='https://gist.github.com/6203d05150de9baf7015.js?file=fiddle.js'></script>
<noscript><pre><code>var favourites = ko.observableArray([
    &quot;chips&quot;,
    &quot;pizza&quot;,
    &quot;lasagne&quot;,
    &quot;curry&quot;]),
    viewModel = valerie.validatableModel({
        &quot;favourites&quot;: favourites,
        &quot;newFavourite&quot;: ko.observable(&quot;new&quot;).validate()
            .string()
            .minimumLength(3)
            .noneOf(favourites)
            .not(&quot;brussel sprouts&quot;)
            .end(),
        &quot;add&quot;: function () {
            favourites.push(viewModel.newFavourite());
        },
        &quot;remove&quot;: function (index) {
            favourites.splice(index(), 1);
        }
    })
        .validateChildProperties()
        .end();

valerie.koBindingsHelper.useValidatingBindingHandlers();

window.onload = function () {
    ko.applyBindings(viewModel, document.getElementById(&quot;sample&quot;));
};</code></pre></noscript></div>
</p>

<h2>CSS</h2>

<p><div><script src='https://gist.github.com/6203d05150de9baf7015.js?file=fiddle.css'></script>
<noscript><pre><code>ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
}

li {
    margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
}

.failed {
    background-color: red;
    color: white;
}

button {
    width: 2em;
}</code></pre></noscript></div>
</p>
